headline: Kraft Heinz: Spinoff Plans Haven't Wowed Me, But Shares Are Cheap
summary: Despite ongoing industry headwinds and Kraft Heinz's weak organic growth, the low valuation and 6% dividend yield offer potential upside. Learn more on KHC stock here.
